###### Presentation of ongoing research on human-AI collaboration for the disinformation detection task concerning several research projects I have acquired throughout the last years (news-polygraph, VERANDA, FakeXplain). Discussing with experts from Germany and the EUREGIO region challenges and upcoming research in the domain of legal compliant and transparent AI systems [Program Link](https://www.euphur.org/en/digital-technologies-en/) 
